Package net.proteusframework.ui.mcolumn

Column based table / tree API.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaseMColumnTableModel.RowDataModel<RT>
    Row data model.
    MTableColumn
    Represents a MIWT table column.
    MTreeColumn
    Represents a MIWT column that can be used in a tree model.

    AbstractColumn
    Convenience implementation of a MTableColumn and MTreeColumn.
    BaseMColumnTableModel<V>
    TableModel that defines it's columns with the MTableColumn interface.
    FixedValueColumn
    Fixed value column.
    MColumnTableModel<V>
    TableModel that defines it's columns with the MTableColumn interface.
    MColumnTreeModel

    MTable<V>
    Table component for column oriented tables.
    MTable.SortableModel
    Sortable model.
    MTree
    Tree component for use with MColumnTreeModel.
    PropertyColumn
    Reflection based column that access the value by property name.

Package net.proteusframework.ui.mcolumn Description

Column based table / tree API.

Helpers for defining TableComponents and TreeComponents based on the columns instead of through the TableModel.
